oai_dc:dc.dc:title: ICOPP: Improved contribution of local feed to support 100% organic feed supply to pigs and poultry
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Nelder, Rebecca
Smith, Jo
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Feeding and growth
Health and welfare
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Project description leaflet in several languages. The aim of ICOPP is to produce economically profitable feeding strategies based on 100% organic feed across Europe, which will supply poultry and pigs the required level of nutrients throughout their lives while supporting high animal health and welfare.
